Hello, the Bot I made removes ads and hidden links in Groups 👨🏻‍✈️

Checks incoming and outgoing messages and even edited messages in a group and deletes if it's an ad🤖

If the group does not have permission to delete messages, the bot will warn the group owner about the ad

After opening the .env file to run the bot
You open the variables named BOT_TOKEN,ADMINS,BOT and run app.py

for example, like this one
BOT_TOKEN=your bot token
ADMINS= your telegram id
BOT=your bot username


<!-- for uzbek -->

Salom men yasagan Bot reklamalarni, yashirin silkalarni Guruhlarda o'chirib beradi 👨🏻‍✈️

Guruhdagi kirdi - chiqdi xabarlarini va hatto tahrirlangan xabarlarni tekshiradi va u reklama boʻlsa oʻchiradi🤖

Agar guruhda botni xabarlarni o'chirishga ruxsati bo'lmasa guruh egasini reklamadan ogohlantiradi

botni ishga tushirish uchun .env fayli ochib keyin 
BOT_TOKEN,ADMINS,BOT nomli o'zgaruvchilar ochib olasiz va app.py ni ishga tushirasiz

